  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505156692\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3234bb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDSSp7fFNniasR1nhuFHMWpbzDY84e9jqFibwtaHsGIfXveUe2mB0JbouA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧 好困</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">这次</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">不仅发布自研编码模型Composer，还重构了IDE交互逻辑，可以最多8个智能体同时跑，早期测试和开发者都说Cursor 2.0真的太快了。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cursor迎来重大升级，2.0版本来了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一直「套壳」的Cursor这次终于发布了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">首款自研编码模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">Composer</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Composer的速度是同等模型的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">4倍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cursor说这是一款专门</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">为低延迟智能编码打造</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">的模型，大部分任务都可以在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">30秒</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">以内完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"315\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5611111111111111\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4e84b04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDGRzdc1BsPEOKRLqhrHaF1iblphngRV87Y6VJ67JrGaUubZOAs7cWIicw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Speed一栏，Composer的速度达到了200 Tokens/秒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了自研模型，Cursor这次重构了交互逻辑，带来了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">多智能体模式</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，在单个提示下，可最多</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">并行运行8个智能体</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">。此功能使用git worktrees或远程机器来防止文件冲突。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"326\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5805555555555556\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=453bd973&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDsibZXkAUj4EicTB0keW8VtAm6Q2R9FuFcuZcfu7MV9olV4xBwp3WND8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次2.0版本还</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">将浏览器嵌入编辑器内</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，这对于前端开发非常友好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以直接选择元素并将DOM信息转发给Cursor。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"326\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5796296296296296\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09337a47&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDuvdM5o3NrbpxVPlR6ic9dm5vD5oXTFNyicV4hSicdjF9J6e9R1VBB3IrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看这个实测，前端开发可以直接在浏览器选定元素，Cursor自动识别对应代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"316\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54f0c0d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDwyvmMWbyY7icOZQbgNmQr4BypLlh7jv9QYcbq5o5A2YgV2vL2cHZPLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次更新还引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">全新的代码审查功能，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">更容易查看 Agent 在多个文件中的所有更改，无需在各个文件之间来回切换。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"468\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8333333333333334\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6ce8fc63&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDNcB01fejvaZPjc2lAMasOPY1Q0Miae4bhjRSeALwDndzg7BO4Db4gPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次一个更大的更新是引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">语音模式（Voice Mode）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，真就是动嘴编程了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"247\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4398148148148148\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=598ae104&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDJE67jE6vKibkIKMYFQAqf8icCVibmPyrqtAYKwrRWMYhaamK25aEJnC8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，改进了带有标记上下文的复制/粘贴提示，已从上下文菜单中</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">移除了许多显式项</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，包括 @Definitions、@Web、@Link、@Recent Changes、@Linter Errors 等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Agent现在可以自我收集上下文，无需在提示输入中手动附加。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"280\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49907407407407406\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=783f7e40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDzmYeOdYicl740DklbFUE47vc4mlQiacNkjXsbQDPc44dFFHzTRf8xFKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cursor一直以来都在「套壳」，虽然作为一家百亿美金估值的公司，却一直没有推出属于自己的模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在过去的时间里，Cursor受困于Claude和其收费模式，导致大部分营收其实都贡献给了Claude等AI模型厂商。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样依赖外部模型的局面，不仅限制了公司的自主创新，也让其在市场中面临着更高的成本和较低的利润空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次Composer的发布意味着Cursor也开始自研模型加入AI大战中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">公司一大做大，自研模型是绝对避不开的一条路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">正如网友所言，不可能百亿美金估值的公司护城河还是个套壳App～</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"316\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5618915159944368\" data-w=\"719\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e784c471&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDhJibTIqtlXN1Ah2Zib7IWZNovaeGGxYnGP511zFicCNEhe4xnD9UWUhcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在刚刚开幕的GTC 2025大会上，老黄特地cue到了Cursor：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0px 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我们英伟达，每一位软件工程师都在用Cursor。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0px 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它就像大家的编程搭档，能够帮忙生成代码，大幅提升生产力。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 48px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:left;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mhcxfrhk24w2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhcv85uub18\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhcxfrhe14vz\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">拓展阅读：</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhcv85uu4nm\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhcxfrhe16bg\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652639699&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c9dfc308bc356a5b829dac88d8d41bf3&amp;token=1759175805&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">「美队」老黄深夜扔出地表最强GPU！算力百倍狂飙，下次改演雷神</span></a></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;body&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">用强化学习打造编程模型</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在软件开发的世界里，速度和智能是永恒的追求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cursor Tab（自研的补全模型）的使用体验就能说明一切。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">很多X上大佬就反馈过，他们最喜欢的还是Cursor Tab功能，既希望模型能瞬间理解编码思路，还要很快的完成编码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">属于是「既要又要」了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"216\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3835616438356164\" data-w=\"730\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=808a2a7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDzRxocJDGtjw1S2AYJvljGF4neN5A7pbFd0TeR3YVxsPrcIkATVtrgw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发者往往希望使用既足够智能又能支持交互式使用的模型，以保持编码的专注与流畅。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cursor早期试验了一个代号为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Cheetah</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">的原型模型，Composer是该模型的更智能升级版，凭借足够的速度支撑交互式体验，让编码始终愉快顺滑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如何既要又要就是Composer需要达到的目的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Composer是一种</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">专家混合（MoE）语言模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，支持长上下文的生成与理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它通过在多样化的开发环境中进行强化学习（RL），对软件工程进行了专项优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">每次训练迭代中，模型都会接收问题描述，并被指示产出最佳响应，无论是代码修改、方案规划，还是信息性回答。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型既能使用读取与编辑文件等简单工具，也能调用更强大的能力，例如终端命令和面向整个代码库的语义搜索。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"315\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ede01846&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDXT1l683Lp2Wcpiahrfz0aBHVWgFibyMbVbCrfDVcm5DyOTnQCUiazAiaGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">强化学习能够有针对性地优化模型，以更好地服务高效的软件工程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">鉴于响应速度是交互式开发的关键，鼓励模型在工具使用上做出高效选择，并在可能的情况下最大化并行处理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，通过减少不必要的回复、避免无依据的陈述来训练模型成为更有帮助的助手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在RL过程中，模型会自发习得一些有用的能力，例如执行复杂搜索、修复linter错误，以及编写并运行单元测试。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"328\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5833333333333334\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"562\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c8f5cf4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3g13T4cwFnicR94DLq21CUDeaedqzK4ewrHlaYDmXwHWe8aGcQibc8IEZa3NnBX4rVtdTvFhyYrs2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">高效训练大型MoE模型需要在基础设施与系统研究方面进行大量投入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;text-align:just